## 🚨 Containment Steps

> **⚡ Execute steps in order. Mark each checkbox as complete. Escalate immediately if any step fails.**

{% if containment_steps is defined and containment_steps %}
{% for step in containment_steps %}
- [ ] **{{ step.name | default("Step") }}** – {{ step.description | default("Execute containment action.") }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- [ ] **Identify and isolate** – Determine affected systems and isolate from the network.
- [ ] **Preserve evidence** – Capture logs, memory dumps, and network traffic before any remediation.
- [ ] **Alert security team** – Notify SOC of the `{{ severity | default("HIGH") }}` severity incident.
- [ ] **Begin investigation** – Assign incident commander and open investigation ticket.
- [ ] **Collect IOCs** – Gather all IPs, domains, file hashes, and behavioural indicators.
- [ ] **Patch or remove vulnerability** – Address the root cause of the incident.
{% endif %}

